\zoli1 \bd Bwana wewe unajua kwamba naweza danganyika duniani kumejaa mapepo mengi na mafundisho ya \bd*\bd Shetani \bd*\bd macho yangu yanatazama na kuyatama aniya masikiyo yanaa sikiliza nataka kudanganyika.\bd*
